Three most popular test runners:
-- unittest          # Build into the Python standard lib 
-- nose2             # Compatible with unittest and will discover all test scripts named with test*.py and testcases.  
-- pytest            # Run all files with test_*.py or *_test.py


Websites:
https://realpython.com/python-testing/
https://nose2.readthedocs.io/en/latest/usage.html
https://pytest.readthedocs.io/en/latest/contents.html

